{
  "stem": "24111.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he found an man, an SR man living in Gratz, which had an restaurant and a pig farm by the name of Schleich.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "S-C-H-L-E-I-C-H.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was actually an Austrian Nazi with the brown shirts, which was called SA.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he had an arrangement with Aron, or with the JUL, that he would take a Jew-- a Jew for 600 mark and send him with-- under the guidance of smugglers he knew, to Yugoslavia.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Aron did send children in the age-- in the age from, let's say 15 to 17, which were orphans, which were actually on his-- under his supervision, in groups of 10, in groups of 8, to Gratz, to this guy by the name of Schleich.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they came to Yugoslavia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I knew a lot of friends of mine, which I saw and-- and had contact with, just were not there anymore the next day or in the-- in the next week when I came.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were not here anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I asked, you know, where's so-and-so, they said, oh, Aron, sent them on this-and-this transport to Yugoslavia.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I had the knowledge already that that existed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not only that, the Jewish-- Aron Menczer had no money.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a very sincere fellow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everything he owned, he gave actually to the children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He worked without salary.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the money he needed to send the children, because Schleich wanted 600 marks per person, Aron got from the Jewish community center, from the Jewish-Israeli [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they paid, actually.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They gave him the money so that he could pay Schleich.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was not Aron Menczer's money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was the collective money of the Jewish community which made it possible [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] for those escapes.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We knew that an large camp exist in Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
